        <!-- Section 2 UI (Understanding Your Needs) -->
        <div id="ui-sec-2" class="fixed top-0 left-0 w-full h-screen z-10 flex pointer-events-none opacity-0">
            <div class="w-[55%] hidden lg:block"></div>
            <div class="w-full lg:w-[45%] flex items-center justify-center p-6 md:pr-16 lg:pr-24 h-full">
                <!-- Clean Embedded Design -->
                <div id="content-card" class="w-full max-w-2xl transform opacity-0 pointer-events-auto mt-20 relative">
                    
                    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-montserrat font-bold text-white mb-6 tracking-tight leading-snug">
                        Understanding Your Needs
                    </h1>
                    
                    <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg mb-10 leading-relaxed font-light">
                        Equi has reached the end of its launch phase. The next phase requires becoming disruption-ready—not only for AI, but for any current or future disruptor.
                    </p>
                    
                    <div class="space-y-5 mb-10 pl-2">
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-pink-500 mt-2.5 shrink-0"></div>
                            <p class="text-gray-400 font-light leading-relaxed">Position Equi for substantive discussions on algorithmic bias.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-pink-500 mt-2.5 shrink-0"></div>
                            <p class="text-gray-400 font-light leading-relaxed">Prepare for AI's impact on core research operations.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-pink-500 mt-2.5 shrink-0"></div>
                            <p class="text-gray-400 font-light leading-relaxed">Build organizational readiness for ongoing disruption.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="border-l-2 border-pink-500 pl-6">
                        <h4 class="text-white font-montserrat font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-xs mb-2">Our Approach</h4>
                        <p class="text-gray-400 font-light leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-base">
                            A structured, three-part engagement that addresses immediate needs while building lasting capability.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Section 3 UI (Disruption Readiness Workshop) -->
        <div id="ui-sec-3" class="fixed top-0 left-0 w-full h-screen z-10 flex pointer-events-none opacity-0">
            <div class="w-[55%] hidden lg:block"></div> 
            <div class="w-full lg:w-[45%] flex items-center justify-center p-6 md:pr-16 lg:pr-24 h-full">
                
                <div id="content-card-3" class="w-full max-w-2xl transform opacity-0 pointer-events-auto mt-20 relative">
                    
                    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-montserrat font-bold text-white mb-6 tracking-tight leading-snug">
                        Disruption Readiness Workshop
                    </h1>
                    
                    <!-- Clean, fixed-height Roll Up Container -->
                    <div class="relative w-full h-[400px] overflow-hidden" style="mask-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, black 80%, transparent 100%); -webkit-mask-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, black 80%, transparent 100%);">
                        <div id="sec-3-inner" class="flex flex-col w-full h-[800px] will-change-transform">
                            
                            <!-- Part 1: Why this matters -->
                            <div class="h-[400px] flex flex-col justify-start shrink-0 pt-2 pr-4">
                                <h3 class="text-white font-montserrat font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-xs mb-3">Why this matters for Equi</h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed font-light mb-4">
                                    Technology-enabled disruption is already established in the context of Equi's work, and in the months and years ahead, innovation with synthetic media and shifts in how trust is attributed online will create new pressures that no organisation can fully, accurately anticipate.
                                </p>
                                <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed font-light mb-8">
                                    The organisations that will navigate multiple and simultaneous disruptions effectively will be ready to transform, shift direction and adapt across the full spectrum of operations — led by leaders who make conscious decisions using structured approaches to interpret new trends and threats.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            
                            <!-- Part 2: Proposed Approach & Outcome -->
                            <div class="h-[400px] flex flex-col justify-start shrink-0 pt-2 pr-4">
                                <h3 class="text-white font-montserrat font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-xs mb-4">Proposed Approach</h3>
                                <div class="space-y-4 mb-8 pl-2">
                                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                                        <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-pink-500 mt-2 shrink-0"></div>
                                        <p class="text-gray-400 font-light leading-relaxed text-sm">Unlock conscious thinking about disruption.</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                                        <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-pink-500 mt-2 shrink-0"></div>
                                        <p class="text-gray-400 font-light leading-relaxed text-sm">Diagnostic assessment with your stakeholders.</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                                        <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-pink-500 mt-2 shrink-0"></div>
                                        <p class="text-gray-400 font-light leading-relaxed text-sm">Use algorithmic bias and AI adoption as live examples.</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                                        <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-pink-500 mt-2 shrink-0"></div>
                                        <p class="text-gray-400 font-light leading-relaxed text-sm">Establish shared view of where Equi stands.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                
                                <div class="border-l-2 border-pink-500 pl-6">
                                    <h4 class="text-white font-montserrat font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-xs mb-2">Outcome</h4>
                                    <p class="text-gray-400 font-light leading-relaxed text-sm">
                                        Strategic framing and confidence to address your priority challenges.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Section 4 UI (Understanding Algorithmic Bias) -->
        <div id="ui-sec-4" class="fixed top-0 left-0 w-full h-screen z-10 flex pointer-events-none opacity-0">
            <div class="w-[55%] hidden lg:block"></div>
            <div class="w-full lg:w-[45%] flex items-center justify-center p-6 md:pr-16 lg:pr-24 h-full">
                
                <div id="content-card-4" class="w-full max-w-2xl transform opacity-0 pointer-events-auto mt-20 relative">
                    
                    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-montserrat font-bold text-white mb-6 tracking-tight leading-snug">
                        Understanding Algorithmic Bias
                    </h1>

                    <!-- Clean, fixed-height Roll Up Container -->
                    <div class="relative w-full h-[400px] overflow-hidden" style="mask-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, black 80%, transparent 100%); -webkit-mask-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, black 80%, transparent 100%);">
                        <div id="sec-4-inner" class="flex flex-col w-full h-[800px] will-change-transform">
                            
                            <!-- Part 1: Why this matters -->
                            <div class="h-[400px] flex flex-col justify-start shrink-0 pt-2 pr-4">
                                <h3 class="text-white font-montserrat font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-xs mb-3">Why this matters for Equi</h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed font-light mb-8">
                                    Algorithmic bias on social media platforms — particularly the disproportionate reach of right-wing and anti-Muslim content — is a live and pressing issue that Equi has been invited to address. Doing so with credibility requires a clear, structured, repeatable and well-governed methodology that helps establish Equi's preferred position in key discussions.
                                </p>
                            </div>

                            <!-- Part 2: Proposed Approach & Outcome -->
                            <div class="h-[400px] flex flex-col justify-start shrink-0 pt-2 pr-4">
                                <h3 class="text-white font-montserrat font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-xs mb-4">Proposed Approach</h3>
                                <div class="space-y-4 mb-8 pl-2">
                                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                                        <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-pink-500 mt-2 shrink-0"></div>
                                        <p class="text-gray-400 font-light leading-relaxed text-sm">Distinguish between coordinated behavior, platform bias, and legitimate engagement patterns.</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                                        <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-pink-500 mt-2 shrink-0"></div>
                                        <p class="text-gray-400 font-light leading-relaxed text-sm">Build evidence base that withstands highest scrutiny.</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                                        <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-pink-500 mt-2 shrink-0"></div>
                                        <p class="text-gray-400 font-light leading-relaxed text-sm">Establish repeatable, well-governed methodology.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                
                                <div class="border-l-2 border-pink-500 pl-6">
                                    <h4 class="text-white font-montserrat font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-xs mb-2">Outcome</h4>
                                    <p class="text-gray-400 font-light leading-relaxed text-sm">
                                        Credible evidence and clear positioning for key discussions on algorithmic bias.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Section 5 UI (AI Capability Development) -->
        <div id="ui-sec-5" class="fixed top-0 left-0 w-full h-screen z-10 flex pointer-events-none opacity-0">
            <div class="w-[55%] hidden lg:block"></div>
            <div class="w-full lg:w-[45%] flex items-center justify-center p-6 md:pr-16 lg:pr-24 h-full">
                
                <div id="content-card-5" class="w-full max-w-2xl transform opacity-0 pointer-events-auto mt-20 relative">
                    
                    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-montserrat font-bold text-white mb-6 tracking-tight leading-snug">
                        AI Capability & Skills Transfer
                    </h1>

                    <!-- Clean, fixed-height Roll Up Container -->
                    <div class="relative w-full h-[400px] overflow-hidden" style="mask-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, black 80%, transparent 100%); -webkit-mask-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, black 80%, transparent 100%);">
                        <div id="sec-5-inner" class="flex flex-col w-full h-[800px] will-change-transform">
                            
                            <!-- Part 1: Why this matters -->
                            <div class="h-[400px] flex flex-col justify-start shrink-0 pt-2 pr-4">
                                <h3 class="text-white font-montserrat font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-xs mb-3">Why this matters for Equi</h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed font-light mb-4">
                                    Equi produces research that is careful, considered and impactful. The people who write it care deeply about the credibility of their work which serves as the foundation of Equi, its reputation and the experience of collaborating on key topics.
                                </p>
                                <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed font-light mb-8">
                                    The cultural moment we're in that Equi's research could shape is evolving so quickly and AI best practices (which are also evolving quickly) could modify how fast and how widely Equi can contribute - potentially making it possible to produce research in a fraction of the time currently required.
                                </p>
                            </div>

                            <!-- Part 2: Proposed Approach & Outcome -->
                            <div class="h-[400px] flex flex-col justify-start shrink-0 pt-2 pr-4">
                                <h3 class="text-white font-montserrat font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-xs mb-4">Proposed Approach</h3>
                                <div class="space-y-4 mb-8 pl-2">
                                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                                        <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-pink-500 mt-2 shrink-0"></div>
                                        <p class="text-gray-400 font-light leading-relaxed text-sm">Map research workflow and identify AI entry points.</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                                        <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-pink-500 mt-2 shrink-0"></div>
                                        <p class="text-gray-400 font-light leading-relaxed text-sm">Understand tools, governance, and risk management.</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                                        <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-pink-500 mt-2 shrink-0"></div>
                                        <p class="text-gray-400 font-light leading-relaxed text-sm">Evidence benefits in real-time through live work.</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                                        <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-pink-500 mt-2 shrink-0"></div>
                                        <p class="text-gray-400 font-light leading-relaxed text-sm">Ensure capability stays with Equi post-engagement.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                
                                <div class="border-l-2 border-pink-500 pl-6">
                                    <h4 class="text-white font-montserrat font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-xs mb-2">Outcome</h4>
                                    <p class="text-gray-400 font-light leading-relaxed text-sm">
                                        Owned AI capability that accelerates research output without compromising quality or credibility.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Section 6 UI (Commercials) -->
        <div id="ui-sec-7" class="fixed top-0 left-0 w-full h-screen z-10 flex pointer-events-none opacity-0">
            <div class="w-full flex items-center justify-center p-6 md:p-16 h-full">
                <div id="content-card-7" class="w-full max-w-5xl pointer-events-auto mt-20">
                    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-montserrat font-bold text-white mb-6 tracking-tight text-center">Commercials & Partnership</h1>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg mb-16 font-light text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">We believe in building lasting relationships. This engagement is designed to establish capability that continues beyond our direct involvement.</p>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 relative z-10">
                        <div class="bg-[#0a0a0a] border border-white/10 border-t-2 border-t-pink-500 p-10 flex flex-col hover:border-pink-500/50 transition-colors shadow-2xl">
                            <h3 class="text-pink-500 font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-xs mb-4">Option 1</h3>
